policies.title: Things to know

html.htmlText: Beautiful, eclectic,  lakeside retreat located on Mason Lake. Two homes on property with total of seven bedrooms, indoor/outdoor hot tubs, dock, deck, boats, 75" big screen TV's and many other amenities. For groups 10 and less rent the main house only -  see listing "Classic Lakeside Home"  as this will reduce the cleaning fee. This listing provides for groups larger than 10 to expand into the guest house that sleeps up to 6. Total number of guests (including all children and infants) is 16.

Main house has 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. Two bedrooms have king size beds, one bedroom has a queen size bed and one bedroom has a full size bed. Daylight basement opens to Lake and covered deck with deck patio furniture and gas fire pit. Upper deck has patio furniture and gas fire pit as well. Wood burning fire pit on the beach area. Large sectional sofas in both main area and in the daylight basement area.

Guest house has three bedrooms each with queen size beds. Great room area with kitchen, living and dining area, deck on both sides of house, gas fireplace in open area. One full bathroom.

Large parking area between both houses can accommodate up to six cars.
Access to all parts of both houses except for one locked storage area in the daylight basement of the main house.
Note that the price of $250/night is for 5 total guests, including all infants and children. Each additional guest is $50/night up to max of 16 in both houses.
